<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Verification Code</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
  <table role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0;">
        <table role="presentation" style="width: 600px; border-collapse: collapse; background-color: #ffffff; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
          
        
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #9C27B0; padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">üîë Verification Code</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
        
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <h2 style="color: #333333; margin-top: 0;">Your One-Time Password</h2>
              
              <p style="color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
                Hello,
              </p>
              
              <p style="color: #555555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
                We received a request that requires verification. 
                Use the code below to complete your action:
              </p>
              
            
              <table role="presentation" style="margin: 30px 0; width: 100%;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e5f5 0%, #e1bee7 100%); padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px;">
                    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px 40px; border-radius: 8px; display: inline-block;">
                      <h1 style="color: #9C27B0; font-size: 42px; letter-spacing: 12px; margin: 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-weight: bold;">
                        {{otp}}
                      </h1>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <p style="color: #777777; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                Enter this code to proceed with your request
              </p>
              
        
              <table role="presentation" style="margin: 30px 0; background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 15px;">
                    <p style="color: #856404; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 14px;">
                      <strong>‚è∞ Time Sensitive:</strong> This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p style="color: #856404; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
                      <strong>üîê Security:</strong> Never share this code with anyone, including our staff.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              
              <table role="presentation" style="margin: 30px 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 6px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <h3 style="color: #333333; margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 16px;">How to use this code:</h3>
                    <ol style="color: #555555; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8;">
                      <li>Return to the verification page</li>
                      <li>Enter the 6-digit code exactly as shown above</li>
                      <li>Complete your action within 10 minutes</li>
                    </ol>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
          
              <table role="presentation" style="margin: 30px 0; background-color: #f8d7da; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 15px;">
                    <p style="color: #721c24; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
                      <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Didn't request this code?</strong> If you didn't request this verification code, 
                      please ignore this email. Your account is still secure.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 30px 0;">
              
              <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
                For your security, we recommend not sharing this code via email or messaging apps.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
        
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
                &copy; {{currentYear}} E-Commerce Store. All rights reserved.
              </p>
              <p style="color: #999999; font-size: 12px; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
                This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>